<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verify Your Flyobo Travel Account</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f6f8;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 24px;
        color: #333;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 620px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }

      .logo {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 28px 0 10px 0;
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4b0082, #6a0dad);
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 32px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin: 0 0 8px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .header p {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin: 0;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 30px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }

      .otp-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 32px 0;
      }

      .otp-code {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #4b0082;
        background: #f3e8ff;
        padding: 18px 40px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 2px dashed #4b0082;
        letter-spacing: 6px;
      }

      .btn-verify {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4b0082, #6a0dad);
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 15px 42px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 17px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 24px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .btn-verify:hover {
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      .warning {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #5a4400;
        background: #fff8e1;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid #ffe28a;
      }

      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #888;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .otp-code {
          font-size: 28px;
          padding: 14px 28px;
          letter-spacing: 4px;
        }

        .btn-verify {
          padding: 12px 28px;
          font-size: 16px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">
        <img
          src="https://flyobo.vercel.app/logo.png"
          alt="Flyobo Travel Logo"
          style="height: 55px"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Flyobo Travel üåç</h1>
        <p>Adventure begins with one click</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>

        <p>
          Thank you for signing up with <strong>Flyobo Travel</strong>! To
          activate your account and start exploring, please verify your email
          using the One-Time Password (OTP) below:
        </p>

        <div class="otp-container">
          <span class="otp-code"><%= otp %></span>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center">
          <a
            href="https://your-frontend-domain.com/activate?email=<%= encodeURIComponent(email) %>&otp=<%= otp %>"
            class="btn-verify"
            >Verify My Account</a
          >
        </div>

        <p class="warning">
          ‚ö†Ô∏è This OTP is valid for <strong>10 minutes</strong>. Please do not
          share it with anyone for your security.
        </p>

        <p>
          If you did not request this email, you can safely ignore it or contact
          our support team for assistance.
        </p>

        <p>
          We're thrilled to have you onboard ‚Äî your next journey is just a click
          away!
        </p>

        <p>
          Best wishes,<br />
          <strong>The Flyobo Travel Team</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Flyobo Travel. All rights
        reserved.<br />
        <small
          >Made with üíú in India | <a href="https://flyobo.vercel.app"
          >flyobo.vercel.app</a
        ></small>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
